    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09041"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1788-01-06">1788  г. 6 генваря.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p> В 4-м действии есть малое прибавление, которое я б желала, чтоб актеры выучили, как скорее, так и лучше.
            <note type="editorial">
                According to A.V. Khrapovitskii's diary, in this note Catherine writes about her comedy <title ref="works.xml#rasstr01">Rasstroennaia sem'ia</title> that was first staged on <date when-custom="1788-01-11">January 11 1788</date> (
                <bibl>
                    <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                    , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 35.</biblScope>
                </bibl>
                ).
            </note></p>
